<div>
  <pre><b><%= $game.own_board_view($game.player_1) %></b></pre>
  <b><u>There are 5 types of ships available to you:</b></u>
  <br>
  <br>
  √ Submarines take up 1 spot.
  <br>
  √ DESTROYERS take 2 spots.
  <br>
  √ Cruisers take 3 spots.
  <br>
  √ Battleships take 4 spots.
  <br>
  √ Aircraft Carriers take 5 spots.
  <br>
  <br>
  <b><u>To place a ship:</b></u>
  <br>
  <br>
  Pick a type:
  <form>
    <select name="ship">
      <option value="submarine">Submarine</option>
      <option value="destroyer">DESTROYER</option>
      <option value="cruiser">Cruiser</option>
      <option vlue="battleship">Battleship</option>
      <option value="aircraft_carrier">Aircraft Carrier</option>
  </select>
  <br>
  <br>
  Enter a coordinate:
  <br>
  <input type="text" name="coordinate">
  <br>
  <br>
  Choose a direction:
  <br>
    <select name="direction">
      <option value=":horizontally">Horizontal</option>
      <option value=":vertically">Vertical</option>
    </select>
  <br>
  <br>
  <input type="submit" value="Submit">
  </form>
</div>